---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "Process";
const description = "Building Your Website, Step by Step";
---

<Layout {title} {description}>
  <section class="my-8 md:mb-12 md:mt-16 max-w-3xl">
    <div>
      <span class="font-medium text-sm uppercase">
        From first message to launch
      </span>
      <h1 class="heading-hero mt-2.5 text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-medium text-balance"> 
        A simple overview of how I usually work with clients.
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section 
    aria-label="Web development process" 
    class="mt-8 md:mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-10"
  >
    <div class="p-2.5 md:p-6 rounded-lg bg-base-300">
      <span class="text-sm">Step 01.</span>
      <h2 class="font-medium mt-2.5 text-3xl">
        Project Request
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 mt-5 text-base-content/70">
        <p>
          First, you send a quick project request. This helps me understand what 
          you need and see if we're a good fit.
        </p>
        <p>
          If it makes sense to move forward, we can hop on a video call or continue 
          the conversation through email or WhatsApp, whatever works best for you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-2.5 md:p-6 rounded-lg bg-base-300">
      <span class="text-sm">Step 02.</span>
      <h2 class="font-medium mt-2.5 text-3xl">
        First Meeting
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 mt-5 text-base-content/70">
        <p>
          (Optional) If you prefer a quick face-to-face before we begin, 
          we can set up a short video call to go over your project, 
          goals, and expectations. It's a good way to make sure we're 
          on the same page and clarify anything upfront.
        </p>
        <p>
          Not into calls? That's totally fine, we can keep it all async via email or chat.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-2.5 md:p-6 rounded-lg bg-base-300">
      <span class="text-sm">Step 03.</span>
      <h2 class="font-medium mt-2.5 text-3xl">
        Proposal
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 mt-5 text-base-content/70">
        <p>
          Once I understand your project, I'll put together <b class="text-base-content">a clear, 
          upfront proposal</b>, no hourly rates, just a flat project price 
          so you know exactly what to expect. No surprises, <b class="text-base-content">just transparency.</b>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-2.5 md:p-6 rounded-lg bg-base-300">
      <span class="text-sm">Step 04.</span>
      <h2 class="font-medium mt-2.5 text-3xl">
        Project Build
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 mt-5 text-base-content/70">
        <p>
          With everything in place, the real work begins. 
          I'll start building your project while keeping you updated along the way.
        </p>
        <p>
          Expect clear communication and regular progress reports through Slack, 
          email, or whatever works best for you. No guesswork, just steady progress.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-2.5 md:p-6 rounded-lg bg-base-300">
      <span class="text-sm">Step 05.</span>
      <h2 class="font-medium mt-2.5 text-3xl">
        Launch
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 mt-5 text-base-content/70">
        <p>
          Once everything is ready, we go live. 
          I'll help make sure the launch is smooth and everything works as expected.
        </p>
        <p>
          After launch, I'm available for fixes, tweaks, or follow-ups if needed.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
